Most liked comment by this Monday wins a free graduation shoot by me and my team! 

The winners package:

- A one on one creative consultation

- Two hour graduation session (must choose between studio or outdoor)
* Two looks
* 5 retouched images

- A short Instagram reel video. (15-30 secs)

Rules: 

- All DC, Maryland, Virginia, and Baltimore Grads may participate.

- The runner up will receive a 50% coupon code towards graduation packages.

- Third place will receive a 25% coupon code towards our graduation packages. 

- Offensive language or profanity will disqualify your comment. 

- Winners will be pinned Monday at 12 pm EST.

- Winners can redeem rewards up until April 30th

Thank you for all your support! May the best comment win

If you’d like to inquire a graduation photoshoot with us between Late March-May, please inquire via www.mkselassi.com/contactus

Get ready to dive into the world of entertainment photography and videography as we discuss insider tips on making your mark and standing out. 

Whether you're an aspiring photographer, videographer, or just curious about the industry, this is your chance to network and chat with the best. 

🗣️ Don't miss out on a night of inspiration, connections, and casual conversations. See you there! 

🗓 Date: Friday, August 11th
🕕 Time:  6-8:30pm
🏢 Venue: Blanche Creative Studio (Alexandria, VA)
